<div class="media stream-item">
  <div class="media-body">

    <div class="section-subheading article-title mb-0 mt-0">
      <a href="/publication/diversity-meta/" >The Relationship Between Team Diversity and Team Performance: Reconciling Promise and Reality Through a Comprehensive Meta-Analysis Registered Report</a>
    </div>

    
    <a href="/publication/diversity-meta/"  class="summary-link">
      <div class="article-style">
        As diversity is becoming increasingly important to organizations, there has been a wealth of research on its relationship to team performance. In this meta-analysis, we synthesize 615 reports (with 2,638 effect sizes) to estimate these relationships, and to test whether their size is substantively meaningful.
      </div>
    </a>
    

    <div class="stream-meta article-metadata">

      

      
      <div>
        

  <span >
      <a href="/author/dr-lukas-wallrich/">Dr Lukas Wallrich</a></span>, <span >
